metadata.name: Flying Formations #1
metadata.description: Flying Formations is the first series in the  Ducks of a Feather project. It is a limited-edition series of 120 one-of-a-kind NFTs created by Tinker Hatfield to benefit University of Oregon Duck Athletes. It represents the initial offering from "Ducks of A Feather" by Division Street, an ongoing marketing initiative featuring University of Oregon athletes.
